---
title: Turkey Cordon Bleu with Baby Tomatoes, Broccolini and Creamy Mash
description: Close your eyes and you'll feel like you're in a restaurant! Cream cheese, cheddar and bacon make a luscious stuffing for golden, breaded turkey breasts in this date night-worthy meal.
